{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_08_03",
  "title": "fran 3話 なんだかんだいい人でしたね",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――舞台初日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――First day on stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "『ふはははは、今更来ても遅いぞ、プカミ達』\n『皆が病で苦しむのを、黙って見ているがいい！』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Hahahaha‚ it's too late‚ Fumika and the others\"\n\"Just watch as everyone suffers from the disease!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "『な……なんだと！？　ワクチン……』\n『病に立ち向かう力を与えるアイテムだと……？』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Wha… What!? Vaccine…\"\n\"An item that gives us the power to fight the disease…?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3999981563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "『おのれ、おのれ、ポンピピン！』\n『くっ、あの時、逃がさずにさえおれば……！！』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Damn‚ damn you‚ Ponpipin!\"\n\"Ugh‚ at that time‚ if I only hadn't missed it…!!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6666648229,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4833.335177100001,
          "startTime": 29.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "『きゃああああーーーー！！』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Ahhhhhーーーー!!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6761662961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.6062364341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（凄いな、小さな子から大人まで大盛り上がりだ）\n（稽古中は本当に、どうなることかと思ったけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Amazing‚ everyone from kids to adults is excited）\n（I really wondered what would happen during rehearsals…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.1333331426
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.3382314445
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.3382314445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "…………え？\n基本的に、私の演技プランで進めていい……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Eh?\nIs it okay to basically go ahead with my… acting plan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4715329887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.3047393561
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "それは、ありがとうございます\nでも、方針転換した理由をお聞かせいただいても？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks‚ a lot\nBut‚ can I tell you why you changed course?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（嘘だろ、優にはあんなに厳しかった蟻田さんが）\n（franさんには、あちらから折れた！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Just kidding‚ Arita-san was so strict with Yu‚）\n（but gave in to fran-san!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.97746106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふん。……他人の意見に耳を傾けようともせず\n自分の考えを押し通そうとするのは、どうかと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm.… without listening to other people's opinions\nit's a bit much to try to push your own thoughts",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "部下の忠告を聞かずに、結局やられてばかりの\nネクロの姿そのものでもある……ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but it's Necro itself‚ who does not listen to the advice of\nher servants and ends up doing only what she wants…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4000018438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0527237973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "私の演技に矯正したいところは山ほどあるけど\nせっかくのネクロらしさを削るのも残念だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are so many things you'd like to improve about my acting‚\nbut didn't want to take away from the Necro-ness that's so precious‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4333351771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "今回だけは例外で、意見を通すことにしたと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so you decided to make an exception this time‚ and go along with my opinion",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0155809166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（つまり、franさんの態度が悪役っぽいから）\n（舞台でもそのままのキャラでいくってことか……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In other words‚ fran-san's attitude is villainous）\n（they'll stick to her character on stage…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7333412806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.3826842866
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、なるほど。それでは、ご期待にお応えしまして\n本番では、もっとネクロになりきってみせますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu‚ I see. Well‚ in response to your expectations‚\nI'll try to act even more like Necro in the show!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1333412806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（褒められてるのかどうかはよく分からないけど……）\n（……まぁ、franさんが納得してるならいいか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm not sure if she's being praised or not…）\n（…Well‚ if fran-san is convinced‚ then it's okay）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.5371800501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――舞台の閉幕後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the stage closed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3555163624,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4477.823074400007,
          "startTime": 125.8333394368
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 122.4555153452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……あー、私ってばなんでも出来ちゃうのよね\nああ、自分の才能が怖いわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… Ahー‚ I can do anything\nAhh‚ I'm scared of my own talent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2666720708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、なんだか嬉しそうですね\n何か、いいニュースでもありましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san‚ you seem so happy\nDid you get any good news?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0000054042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、『ぷりエン』の舞台の講評が上がってたんです\n演劇の評論家だか、結構偉い人が書いたみたいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ the review of the show \"Pretty★Angel\" was up\nIt seems to have been written by a theater critic or some other pretty great person",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.1666720708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "好評だった第一弾を踏まえての次回作は\n往々にして高まった期待を超えられないものだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Set on the acclaimed first installment‚\nthe sequel often fails to live up to the high expectations…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1333163578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "今作はその不安を払拭し、さらなる広がりを見せた\nそれは敵側のドラマもきちんと描いたことにより……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This work overcomes such concerns and shows a more advanced appearance\nAnd that's because it properly depicted the villain's side of the story…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.0333163578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "ね？　私のこと、べた褒めじゃないです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right? They're raving about me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.8529075547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。俺から見ても、いい舞台でしたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. In my opinion‚ it was a good show",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.9335423076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でも稽古の最終日まで、蟻田さんと言い合ってたので\n見守るこっちは気が気じゃなかったですけどね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But until the last day of rehearsals‚ you were arguing with Arita-san\nand I was worried and didn't know what to do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.0666496912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "あれはクリエイター同士のぶつかり合いってやつですよ\nいいものを作るためには、妥協は出来ないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the kind of clash between creators‚ you know\nTo make something good‚ you can't compromise",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.2999830245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "今思えば、蟻田さんもなんだかんだいい人でしたね\nまた一緒に仕事してもいいかなーってくらいには",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking back‚ Arita-san was a good person‚ after all\nI'd probably like to work with himー again",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.3333153406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "喉元過ぎればって感じですね\n稽古中は毎日、楽屋で愚痴を言ってたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Danger past‚ God forgotten\nYou complained to me in the dressing room‚ every day during rehearsals",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.2333072025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、トリエル……と言うかすみれが気疲れしてたので\n次があれば、もうちょっと控えめにお願いします……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ TRINITYAiLE… I mean Sumire‚ she was exhausted‚\nso if there's a next time‚ please be more polite…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.9666517257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "善処しまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll think about itー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.955086335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あと、そういえば。『ぷりエン』の舞台の運営から\n当初の予定にはなかったお金まで振り込まれてたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ by the way. I received some money from the \"Pretty★Angel\" stage production company\nthat wasn't originally planned",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.6666496912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "その振込の内訳は「ネクログッズのマージン」と\nあったんですが、franさんは何かご存じですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The breakdown of that transfer was listed as 「Margin of Necro goods」‚\nDo you know anything about that‚ fran-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.8333122889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええと……ネクロを演じたのは私なんですから\n私にもマージンが入るのは当然では？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-Umm… I played Necro‚\nso surely I should get a margin too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.1666415532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "お金くれるなら、もらっとけばいいじゃないですか\nボーナスだ、ラッキーってことで。私もほしいですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they're giving me money‚ I might as well take it\nIt's a bonus‚ lucky. I want it too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.4333082199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "だとしても、契約はちゃんとしないと後で困りますから\n三枝さんにも伝えて、書面を交わしてもらわないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ if we don't get the contract right‚ it'll cause problems later\nI need to tell Saegusa-san and get it in writing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.6999738693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor022.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……さ、三枝さんにも、話すんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… Y-you mean you're going to tell Saegusa-san too…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.888675154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そのつもりですが、それが何か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ but what's the problem?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.4489698458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor023.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、その……ほら、私が意見して\n衣装デザインを、少し変えたじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ look…… hey look‚ I suggested an idea\nand changed the costume design a little bit‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.3333021164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor024.m4a",
      "text": "舞台版の衣装もグッズ化して販売するって聞いたので\nなら私にもデザイン料入らないんですかって言ったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard that the stage costumes will be sold as goods\nSo I asked if I wouldn't get a design fee‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.4999362309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor025.m4a",
      "text": "プロデューサーが売上の一部を私にも回してくれるって\n……ですので決して、怪しいお金じゃないんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and the producer said he'd give me a portion of the sales\n…So‚ absolutely‚ it is not suspicious money!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.7332899093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、それはありがたい話ですが\nでも……なんで、それを俺にも黙ってたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ that's a nice story‚\nBut… why didn't you keep that from me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.6666232426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor026.m4a",
      "text": "だってそしたら、マネジメント費用とか言って、事務所\nにも何割か余分に持っていかれちゃうじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I said that‚ the office would have to take\na certain percentage extra‚ calling it management fees!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 304.399956576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……それも三枝さんに報告しておきますね\nfranさんがうちとの契約内容に不満があるようだと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand… I'll report that to Saegusa-san as well\nfran-san is unhappy with the terms of our contract",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 313.0332736332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor027.m4a",
      "text": "いやー、勝手に話進めたのは反省してますから\nそれはやめてーー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heyー‚ I regret going ahead with this without your permission\nPlease stop thatーー!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 321.2666069666,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}